data.description: Pride of Ownership shown in this spacious, just over 1,800 square foot, single owner property with Two Owner Suites, Two Bathrooms, and a Two Car garage.  Bright and open Living Room with access to back patio.  Kitchen and breakfast nook, offer lots of counter and storage space with a full wall of cabinetry. Fully landscaped back yard with a covered patio and a Rock Water feature.
